            "description": "Regional study of the reservoir properties and distribution, and charge potential of the Sgiath Formation around Nexen's producing assets in the Inner Moray Firth. \nMy focus was on interpretation of regional geology, facies interpretation and reservoir characterisation (from core and well-log data), facies distribution prediction, uncertainty analysis, and risking. Extensive use was made of OpenWorks, Petrel and ArcGIS to create and analyse a regional database of rock properties derived from core and log analysis, other well data, and information obtained from scientific publications.\n",
